{"tid":408430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【海軍爆醜聞】最先進驅逐艦「南京號」 政委蛇王酗酒窒息死　","createTime":"2017-09-21T08:07:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-21T11:06:11.000Z","uid":47272,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7e28d67f95cff7ae50a0f13096112dd7cd58032","tid":408430,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170921&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57237403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170921%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57237403&d=MhMkvgyz0adl4zSqwv%2B4ddU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bab067fb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170921%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D57237403&h=f0cd7c88\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170921&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=57237403</a><br />\n中國海軍最先進的052D型導彈驅逐艦155艦「南京號」，還未服役，已爆出軍紀問題。微信今日瘋傳一份通報指，155艦政委（相當於軍隊中的黨委書記）黃紅飛，在未有按規定請假，擅自參與船廠老闆所設的聚餐，席間酗酒，致嘔吐物倒流窒息身亡。解放軍高層極為緊張，已下令徹查事件。<br />\n<br />\n據該分通報所指，事發於本月4日晚，半島船業有限公司董事長任國定邀請東海艦隊原副參謀長皮國湧（2009年7月退休），在浙江省舟山實君廷大酒店聚餐，並安排3名地方人員作伴。皮國湧又邀請一批舊部屬及友人，並由其任職155艦副艦長的兒子皮率出面，邀請了155艦實習艦長朱恒、155艦政委黃紅飛及549艦政委張貴堂出席聚餐。皮率自己還邀請了549艦反潛長張雲鵬和一名地方人員參加。<br />\n<br />\n但朱恒、黃紅飛並未按規定請假，而張貴堂只口頭向所屬軍艦的艦長作出請示。當晚聚餐共飲用6瓶500毫升53度的白酒和10罐330毫升的啤酒。隨後，黃紅飛返回單位，因酒後嘔吐物倒流到氣管導致窒息死亡。事發後，軍方高層極為緊張，軍委副主席許其亮更批示要「查明原因，查清責任，汲取教訓，嚴格管理。」<br />\n<br />\n有指黃紅飛曾任東海艦隊「莆田艦」政委。而155艦是江南造船廠承建的第9艘052D型導彈驅逐艦，2015年下水，預計明年正式服役。有分析指，這是海軍中將沈金龍今年1月接掌海軍司令員後第一宗重大事故。"},{"pid":"2b940d77f08bef6bcc16f10239c000c27157699a","tid":408430,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/l75yhu4j\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fl75yhu4j&h=103207bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53152b0e37ee9c148c51a3ef6bed821dcb91a75f","tid":408430,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:10:52.000Z","msg":"銀樣乜乜乜"},{"pid":"7d5e85675adbb53fc419c7ab43651d6f0334eaeb","tid":408430,"uid":46454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"過左成百年都仲要重蹈北洋艦隊的覆轍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6175d0546eaf3359e01c97bce665bc9c3eeb2e","tid":408430,"uid":2521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:11:44.000Z","msg":"近排D茅台平<br />\n應該係入多左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c29a2e98b26f8346cbb6374e382394e2ed993b20","tid":408430,"uid":8493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:13:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://sites.google.com/site/sanhumanity/_/rsrc/1318564956449/ze/zhu-huan/1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fsanhumanity%2F_%2Frsrc%2F1318564956449%2Fze%2Fzhu-huan%2F1.JPG&h=efba8def&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a19734fae66522daf44edf3acfdee54e7b47ec6","tid":408430,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"北洋艦隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f519de670eecd55161506332bb1e32e3a9cec5c","tid":408430,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:20:47.000Z","msg":"白酒定消毒火酒啊？"},{"pid":"01abc00b2c20949a0541bd456eec648772ec43a8","tid":408430,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T10:29:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/sanhumanity/_/rsrc/1318564956449/ze/zhu-huan/1.JPG&quot;\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsites.google.com%2Fsite%2Fsanhumanity%2F_%2Frsrc%2F1318564956449%2Fze%2Fzhu-huan%2F1.JPG%2